graph TD
    Start([开始]) --> NotStarted["not_started<br/>(状态码: 0)"]
    
    NotStarted -->|正常流程| Live["live"]
    NotStarted -->|延迟| Delayed["delayed<br/>(状态码: 61)"]
    NotStarted -->|取消| Cancelled["cancelled<br/>(状态码: 70)"]
    
    Delayed -->|恢复| NotStarted
    
    Live -->|短期中断| Interrupted["interrupted<br/>(状态码: 80)"]
    Live -->|正常结束| Ended["ended<br/>(状态码: 100)"]
    Live -->|加时赛结束| AET["aet<br/>(状态码: 110)"]
    Live -->|点球结束| Penalties["match_after_penalties<br/>(状态码: 120)"]
    Live -->|取消| CancelledLive["cancelled<br/>(创建新ID)"]
    
    Interrupted -->|恢复| Live
    Interrupted -->|长期中断| Suspended["suspended<br/>(状态码: 81)"]
    
    Suspended -->|恢复| Live
    Suspended -->|推迟| Postponed["postponed<br/>(状态码: 60)"]
    
    Postponed -->|>3天: 创建新ID| Start
    Postponed -->|1-2天: 同ID转换| NotStarted
    
    Ended -->|结果确认| Closed["closed"]
    AET -->|结果确认| Closed
    Penalties -->|结果确认| Closed
    
    Ended -->|仅直播覆盖| EndedFinal["ended<br/>(最终状态)"]
    
    Closed --> End([完成])
    EndedFinal --> End
    CancelledLive --> End
    
